					<p><strong>Lessons Learned: </strong></p>
					<ul>
					<li>Change management is the biggest challenge. </li>
					<li>Communication matters: You communicate easily too much or not enough or too late. You need always to search for a right balance.</li> 
					<li>The involvement of and listening to employees was a key factor of success for the project.</li> 
					<li>Clear vision and strategy coming from the top of the FPS.</li>
					</ul>


